Package com.pranab.playwithgraphs.datastructure

Interface LinkedList<V>

Type Parameters:
V - - The generic type, whose objects will be maintained in collection
All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<V>, List<V>
All Known Implementing Classes:
DynamicList
public interface LinkedList<V>
extends List<V>
An ordered collection. The collection preserves the order of insertion and is optimized for quick insertion and deletion.
Author:
Pranab Bharadwaj
